  "instructions": [
    "Bring salted water to a boil in a large pot; cook pasta until al dente, about 8-10 minutes.",
    "While pasta cooks, whisk almond butter, almond milk, lemon juice, olive oil, and 1 tsp salt in a bowl until smooth.",
    "Reserve 1 cup pasta water; drain pasta and return to pot.",
    "Pour almond sauce over pasta; toss, adding reserved pasta water a tablespoon at a time until sauce coats noodles.",
    "Stir in chopped dill, sliced olives, crumbled feta, and spinach; cook for 2 minutes until spinach wilts.",
    "Season with pepper; adjust salt as needed.",
    "Plate and drizzle extra olive oil; serve immediately."
